description: This Chainlink VRF hall of fame Plezier purrs with a rating of 50, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 250, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, 8 for East, Leverage for South, and 5 for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/70505-88654-2.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [250 Votes, Hall of Fame]
